divs: Sighting Detailsi was taking pictures of airplane contrails ovr my house. The next morning I was looking over my pictures, when I noticed an unusual object in the photo. I saw nothing unusual in the sky at the time i took the picture. I would have noticed something, I think, as my attention was directed on the sky. I don't recall hearing any noise or unusual sound. I have no idea what this thing is, not a bird, or bug, it certainly isn't a airplane or helicopter. I showed the photo to my wife, who is VERY skeptical of any kind of "paranormal" stuff.She couldn't figure out what it was, or could be. I took the photo with my iphone's 12 megapixel camera. I don't think I was using the zoom. I have sent this picture, via email, to Mr. Robert Gardner, who is in charge of these things in my part of Pennsylvania. It was his request that i fill out this report,
